[18/06/2019 18:39:35] <font color="#00ff00">como pasta o arroz basmati.</font>
[18/06/2019 18:39:37] <font color="#00ff00">¿Y la mitad restante?</font>
[18/06/2019 18:39:38] <font color="#00ff00">Verduras.</font>
